About this item

Product details

The Maverick 7-ft Pool Table delivers top quality billiards with the extra bonus of table tennis - all at this great price! If you love to play pool, this table has quality features and the compact 7 foot playing surface fits in many game rooms where a larger table won't. Double the fun with the included table tennis table top! Includes all the accessories you need to play pool and table tennis. Add this versatile Hathaway game table to your rec room for hours of gaming fun! Your item comes with a 180-day limited warranty

Hathaway Maverick 7-Foot Pool and Table Tennis Multi Game with Red Felt and Blue Table Tennis Surface, Cues, Paddles and Balls:

  • Pool Table playfield: 74.75-in L x 36.75-in W x 5/8-in thick MDF with durable high quality red felt
  • Table Tennis playfield: 84-in L x 46-in W x 1/2-in thick blue two-piece top with black edge trim
  • Silver laminate top rail with 1/2-in white inlay sights and chrome-plated corner cap
  • Reinforced rubber cushions provide accurate and fast ball rebound
  • Black matte laminated side and end panels with black ABS molded corner connectors
  • L-shaped leg design with leg levelers for added stability
  • Durable, ABS molded drop pockets

    Excellent pool and ping pong table
    There is minimal assembly required for this table - you will add the legs and supports. Assembling this table was straight forward and easy as long as you are fastidious and patient. We used a battery operated drill to screw in the screws where we could, thus saving some time. Once all the parts were assembled, we added the adjustable feet, turned down all the way.
